{"tid":1976040,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感(2)","createTime":"2020-04-17T03:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T12:59:44.000Z","uid":26846,"like":8,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e7219f45f9b4901d473c3271e9269adc47302f","tid":1976040,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:18:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">之前個post爆左，依家再開，通街都係處#48083 依條仆街泛民打手日日幫泛民護航，成日以為自己好撚風趣，周圍搞分化搞事非，真係頂佢唔撚順。</span><br />\n<br />\n人哋最睇重支旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你想人幫手<br />\n咪用英文寫slogan<br />\n但唔好搞人枝旗<br />\n你又唔係美國佬舉乜撚美國旗<br />\n鬼佬見到只會反感<br />\n英國旗仲有得拗吓<br />\n<br />\n咪撚信共諜陳雲<br />\n出屎穚玩爛件事<br />\n<br />\nby通街都係處  9個月前"},{"pid":"aa3426ccfa4ec31d1ab2b66bdd9ab511eb1aba76","tid":1976040,"uid":26846,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:19:34.000Z","msg":"唔好舉美國旗"},{"pid":"40079fba7d5fde5c5c35a256cbedf00683dba636","tid":1976040,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e15c8744c51c2a0f1795d2074621ba57a93fa3e","tid":1976040,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237604b112d792ffdb16d995ddb81a8c9dca5327","tid":1976040,"uid":95138,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:26:37.000Z","msg":"又binc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148847f516b5c3f23dfbdca3e07096d477ed94a8","tid":1976040,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:28:06.000Z","msg":"依條撚樣 7到仆街 都係要出黎刷存在"},{"pid":"44b3fdeb5004b25907d511b2dc32082a5a9be197","tid":1976040,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid